docs.lead_paragraph: MONTEVIDEO, June 22.--A violent gale which began shortly after midnight reached a maximum velocity of eighty-three miles an hour at 5:23 o'clock this morning and continued all day, demoralizing shipping and causing considerable damage ashore, especially to electric light and telephone wires.
